  "prompt": "What are the the most consumed meats in the world?",
  "response": "The most consumed meats in the world are:\n\n1. **Poultry**: Chicken, in particular, is the leading meat consumed globally due to its affordability, versatility, and lower environmental impact compared to red meats.\n2. **Pork**: Widely consumed in many countries, especially in East Asia, Europe, and parts of the Americas. Pork is favored for its variety of cuts and uses in different cuisines.\n3. **Beef**: Beef is popular in the United States, Brazil, Argentina, and many other countries. It is prized for its flavor and is commonly used in steaks, roasts, and ground beef products.\n4. **Lamb and Goat**: These meats are particularly popular in the Middle East, North Africa, parts of Europe, and certain regions of Asia.\n\nConsumption patterns can vary significantly based on cultural, economic, and dietary preferences.",
